{"code":0,"message":"","data":null,"sentence":{"phonemes":[],"text":"I met a girl even more melancholic than you. She said she misses your cat form. I cannot bear to see others shed tears. So I journeyed far, killed the magician, and came to bring you back.","words":[]}}
